              "id": "CVE-2025-4878-libssh",
              "name": "RpmMatcherExactDirectMatch",
              "shortDescription": {
                "text": "CVE-2025-4878 low vulnerability for libssh package"
              },
              "fullDescription": {
                "text": "A vulnerability was found in libssh, where an uninitialized variable exists under certain conditions in the privatekey_from_file() function. This flaw can be triggered if the file specified by the filename doesn't exist and may lead to possible signing failures or heap corruption."
